  "text": "By nesting ♦ operators as in φ * , we force the counting propositions [CITATION_1] and cp 2 = [G 2 , 3] to be satis ed in given order. As we increase h, we also increase the number of counting propositions to be satis ed in a given order. For example, for three goals, φ * is given as follows:",
